<div class="my-4 d-flex steps3_div flex-wrap">
<div class="identity_verification_div mb-2">
<p class="step-div-heading">Identity Verification</p>
<p class="description">The easiest way to verify your identity is to provide a color copy of the front and back of your state issued driver's license or ID card.</p>
</div>
<div class="identity_verification_div mb-2">
<p class="step-div-heading">Employment Verification Form</p>
<p class="description">You must give this document to your employer to complete and submit to Aflac in order to verify your eligibility for the program.</p>
</div>
<div class="identity_verification_div mb-2">
<p class="step-div-heading">Additional supporting documents</p>
